main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Wilmington, Ohio on September 28, 1966, involving a round-oval shaped object observed in the eastern sky.
interesting points: The observed object had an apparent ring that would disappear and reappear,The observer contacted local authorities but found no previous reports of unusual sightings,The FAA reported no unusual observations at the time,The object seemed to change its position relative to itself during the sighting,Several other individuals in the area were also impressed by the unusual characteristics of the object.
sighted object: a round-oval shaped object with an apparent ring
witness description: a 47-year-old male who observed the object, noting its behavior and characteristics
